          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>The <fr:em><fr:strong>fiber</fr:strong></fr:em> of a function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex> at an element <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b:B]]></fr:tex> is the type consisting of elements <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a\colon  A]]></fr:tex> equipped with identifications <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p\colon  fa=b]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
